<FlowDocument xmlns="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2006/xaml/presentation"
             FontSize="14" FontFamily="Georgia">
	<Paragraph>
		<Image Source="/ReflectionStudio;component/Resources/Images/128x128/reflection_studio.png" Width="40"></Image>
		<Bold>Reflection Studio</Bold>
	</Paragraph>
	<Paragraph>
		<Run FontSize="13" FontWeight="Bold">
			Welcome to Reflection Studio. It is a development tool that encapsulate all my work around reflection, performance and software quality.
		</Run>
		<LineBreak/>
		<LineBreak/>
		<Run FontSize="11">In a short way, here under is what i planned to include in it :</Run>
	</Paragraph>
	<List>
		<ListItem>
			<Paragraph>
				<Run FontSize="12" FontWeight="Bold">
					Performance
				</Run>
				<LineBreak/>
				<Run FontSize="11">With Reflection Studio, you can create a performance project. It enable to inject and analyse performance traces into any NET assemblies
					to optimize the code based on it's execution.
				</Run>
				<LineBreak/>
			</Paragraph>
		</ListItem>
		<ListItem>
			<Paragraph>
				<Run FontSize="12" FontWeight="Bold">
					Assembly
				</Run>
				<LineBreak/>
				<Run FontSize="11">
					Reflection Studio contains an assembly explorer like Reflector. It allow you to discover assembly content and is associated with a class diagram
					document to generated architecture oriented schema. 
				</Run>
				<LineBreak/>
			</Paragraph>
		</ListItem>
		<ListItem>
			<Paragraph>
				<Run FontSize="12" FontWeight="Bold">
					Database
				</Run>
				<LineBreak/>
				<Run FontSize="11">
					Reflection Studio contains a database explorer like SQL Server management studio (based on a schema and plugin system).
					The actual SQL Server 2K plugin allow to discover the schema, generate, modify and execute scripts, view dependencies, control the quality by generating a report.
				</Run>
				<LineBreak/>
			</Paragraph>
		</ListItem>
		<ListItem>
			<Paragraph>
				<Run FontSize="12" FontWeight="Bold">
					Code generation
				</Run>
				<LineBreak/>
				<Run FontSize="11">
					Reflection Studio also contains a template explorer associated with a code generator engine which allow to automatically create
					code based on the associated database. One editor allow you to create the template code, compile and test the code generated.
				</Run>
				<LineBreak/>
			</Paragraph>
		</ListItem>
	</List>
	<Paragraph FontSize="11">
		<Run FontSize="11">
			Start a new performance project :
		</Run>
